answer_llm:
If you encounter a Docker Temporary failure in name resolution during the Serverless Deep Learning section, you should add the next lines to vim /etc/docker/daemon.json:
{
"dns": ["8.8.8.8", "8.8.4.4"]
}
Then, restart docker using the command: sudo service docker restart.

